<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .proposal-title {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .cta-link {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 8px 0 20px;
            color: #0066cc;
            word-break: break-all;
        }
        .divider {
            border: none;
            border-top: 2px solid #ddd;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .lang-label {
            font-size: 0.75em;
            color: #999;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    {% set call_title = object.call.title if object.call else '' %}

    <p class="lang-label">Deutsch</p>

    <p>Hi {{ reviewer.username }}!</p>

    <p>Du wurdest gebeten, die Einreichung <span class="proposal-title">"{{ object.title }}"</span>{% if call_title %} für <span class="proposal-title">"{{ call_title }}"</span>{% endif %} zu begutachten.</p>

    <p>Du kannst die Einreichung unter folgendem Link einsehen und dein Gutachten abgeben:</p>

    <a class="cta-link" href="{{ proposal_url }}">{{ proposal_url }}</a>

    <hr class="divider">

    <p class="lang-label">English</p>

    <p>Hi {{ reviewer.username }}!</p>

    <p>You have been asked to review the submission <span class="proposal-title">"{{ object.title }}"</span>{% if call_title %} for <span class="proposal-title">"{{ call_title }}"</span>{% endif %}.</p>

    <p>You can view the submission and submit your review at the following link:</p>

    <a class="cta-link" href="{{ proposal_url }}">{{ proposal_url }}</a>
</body>
</html>
